{"tid":2128595,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何柏良：做好防疫措施的話 舉行選舉問題不大 政府豁免檢疫處理不當 或危害國家安全","createTime":"2020-07-28T05:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T05:33:03.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"06503cc4a3a41a9b71634f3f1299418f0fca95f2","tid":2128595,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:22:38.000Z","msg":"港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良在電台節目表示，鄰近疫情較嚴重的國家可以舉行選舉，相信做好防疫措施問題不大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2533493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2533493&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBhq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=7442acd7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2533493</a><br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良在電台節目表示，沒想到政府未有統計豁免檢疫人士數目，相關豁免配套亦做得不清不楚，如處理不當，可能會將病毒透過跨境人士帶回內地，或會危害國家安全，認為政府要優先為最多人數的豁免檢疫類別做檢測，同時加強執法。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良認為，政府再收緊防疫措施是無可奈何，相信可阻斷傳播鏈，又指本港檢疫安排太多不足，建議應徵用全間酒店作檢疫中心，現時的檢疫中心轉做處理輕症病人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2533487\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2533487&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBhq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=a08003a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2533487</a><br />\n<br />\n咩電台既節目<br />\n想聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8ef1f5b48720c1089dca38c2f720e0df22213f","tid":2128595,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:33:03.000Z","msg":"國家安全 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}